msgstr "“这东西有能力终结数十万有机生命的性命，你应该使用它。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:64
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_AEA_KING\"]/text-"
"aea-alternative"
